      "updated": 1781654867863,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "A deck of cards that\ndeals to players. The\ndeck's methods allow it\nto be shuffled, allow it\nto deal cards and allow\ncards to be drawn.",
      "fontSize": 16,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "A deck of cards that deals to players. The deck's methods allow it to be shuffled, allow it to deal cards and allow cards to be drawn.",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "APBZKQbfGw6bTNm_rEqi9",
